{
  "stem": "1537.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, and there, they make places there to sleep, and then from there, you know, you get organized and you see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the train stops in Somotor-- dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You couldn't see an inch, so dark, because there's no electricity, nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm going down the train and I hear talking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They're talking Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, I go there, who are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, who are you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Say, I'm Hershel Reuben.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hershel Reuben?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then there's another cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there's a Spiegel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About five of us, we arrive the same time, on the same train, without knowing each other, that we are on the same train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So where you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You go to my cousin there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody goes there, first to spend the evening on the floor, it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in the morning, we going to see what we have to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I'm going down, our house is the first house from the railroad station, because that's where we had the tavern.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went down the street and I look the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The weeds up to the roof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Windows broken out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is terrible, look at this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where I was born.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's nothing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just make a right turn, you know, and I'm going to my cousin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We come there, we open the door, so everybody's happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hershel, you know, where were you, where were you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I tell them the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Meckel, the same like I had a brother Meckel who died of appendix infection.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was too late for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I tell him, Meckel, your brother Mordecai, he was with me, and I helped him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had it not bad on the end, and I fed him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
